<div id="weight-step" class="quiz-step" style="display: none;">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4" id="weight-title">
        Hvad er din vægt?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        Vægt hjælper os med at bestemme det rigtige fasthedsniveau og støtte for optimal komfort.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div id="weight-inputs" class="mb-6 space-y-4">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <label for="weight1" class="text-base font-medium block" id="weight1-label">
          Din vægt (kg)
        </label>
        <input
          id="weight1"
          type="number"
          placeholder="Indtast vægt i kg"
          min="35"
          max="180"
          class="quiz-input h-12 text-center text-lg"
          oninput="futonQuiz.updateWeight('person1', this.value)"
        />
      </div>

      <div id="weight2-container" class="space-y-2" style="display: none;">
        <label for="weight2" class="text-base font-medium block">
          Person 2 vægt (kg)
        </label>
        <input
          id="weight2"
          type="number"
          placeholder="Indtast vægt i kg"
          min="35"
          max="180"
          class="quiz-input h-12 text-center text-lg"
          oninput="futonQuiz.updateWeight('person2', this.value)"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-muted/30 rounded-2xl p-4 mb-6">
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-lightbulb"><path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5"/><path d="M9 18h6"/><path d="M10 22h4"/></svg>
        Din vægtinformation hjælper os med at anbefale det rigtige fasthedsniveau for korrekt rygradsjustering og komfort.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-between">
      <button class="quiz-btn quiz-btn-secondary h-10 px-4" onclick="futonQuiz.prevStep()">
        Tilbage
      </button>
      <button 
        id="weight-next-btn"
        class="quiz-btn quiz-btn-primary h-10 px-4" 
        onclick="futonQuiz.nextStep()"
        disabled
      >
        Fortsæt
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>